import { useEffect } from "react" import { Link, useParams } from "react-router-dom" import { useFetchContactsQuery } from "../../storeRTK/store" function FormList() { const { data, refetch } = useFetchContactsQuery() const params = useParams() useEffect(() => { const findItem = data.find((item)=>{ return item.id === params.id }) console.log(findItem); }, [params]) return
